      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "FULL NOISE (8) goes very well here starting six times for two wins and three minors. Hit the frame latest (26.18) when third at this track in a Grade 4/5. Rates a leading player. LAMINATE (1) has a fair record and proved too classy last time to win by 3.5 lengths at Warrnambool in a handy 25.56 beating Black Tycoon. Recorded one of the quickest times on the card in scoring last start. Bold showing expected again. BALLANTYNE STAR (2) tends to drift back and work into the race, finishing out of the placings two back before charging home into the minors latest when third (25.95) in a Grade 5 at Warrnambool last time. Solid record at the distance winning three races. Has never missed the frame from three starts from this draw, including a win. Expected to be in the finish again. HANDSOME RATIO (7) will give backers a sight.",
